_comment:
Manual overrides + ignore list for QB invoices/bills. qb_sync.py applies these BEFORE its heuristic matching. Use any combination:

  invoice_overrides / bill_overrides  — {"QB Invoice/Bill Id": "project_number"}
  customer_project / vendor_project   — {"name substring": "project_number"}
  ignore_invoice_ids / ignore_bill_ids — ["id", ...]  (drop the record entirely from dashboard + unmatched list)
  ignore_customer_patterns / ignore_vendor_patterns — ["name substring", ...]  (drop any record whose customer/vendor matches)

For 'ignore_*' entries, the invoice/bill is fully skipped — it doesn't appear on the dashboard and won't show up in the reconciliation list.
